.label {{
    font: 12px sans-serif;
    pointer-events: none;
    text-shadow: 0 1px 0 #fff, 1px 0 0 #fff, 0 -1px 0 #fff, -1px 0 0 #fff;
}}
```
The text shadow creates a white outline around the labels, making them more readable against the background.

With these changes, the labels should now be visible and positioned correctly relative to their corresponding nodes.

